I18N4Vaadin is a small add-on for Vaadin intented to make it easier to create localized applications.
Version 2.0 is designed for Vaadin 7 and CDI.

BUILDING I18N4Vaadin 2.0
------------------------

In order to build I18N4Vaadin, you need Java SDK 6 and Maven 3.

Fire up a command line and execute the following commands:

  $ cd parent
  $ mvn install
  

USING I18N4Vaadin 2.0
---------------------

Documentation has not been written yet as the project is still in alpha-stage.
  
